#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:2
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Features"
msgstr "Druge zmožnosti"

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:4
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other &umbrello; Features"
msgstr "Druge zmožnosti &umbrello;"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:5
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This chapter will briefly explain some other features &umbrello; offers you."
msgstr ""
"To poglavje bo na kratko razložilo nekatere druge zmožnosti, ki vam jih "
"ponuja &umbrello;."

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:7
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copying objects as PNG images"
msgstr "Kopiranje predmetov kot slik PNG"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:8
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Apart from offering you the normal copy, cut and paste functionality that "
"you would expect to copy objects between different diagrams, &umbrello; can "
"copy the objects as PNG pictures so that you can insert them into any other "
"type of document. You do not need to do anything special to use this "
"feature, just select an object from a diagram (Class, Actor, &etc;) and copy "
"it (<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></keycombo>, or using the menu), then "
"open a <application>Calligra Words</application> document (or any program "
"into which you can paste images) and select <guimenuitem>Paste</"
"guimenuitem>. This is a great feature to export parts of your diagram as "
"simple pictures."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega, da vam ponuja običajno funkcijo kopiranja, izrezovanja in "
"lepljenja, ki bi jo pričakovali pri kopiranju predmetov med različnimi "
"diagrami, &umbrello; lahko kopira predmete kot slike PNG, tako da jih lahko "
"vstavite v katero koli drugo vrsto dokumenta. Za uporabo te funkcije vam ni "
"treba storiti ničesar posebnega, samo izberite predmet iz diagrama (Razred, "
"akter, &etc;) in ga kopirajte (<keycombo>&Ctrl;<keycap>C</keycap></"
"keycombo>, ali z uporabo menija), nato odprite dokument "
"<application>Calligra Words</application> (ali kateri koli program, v "
"katerega lahko prilepite slike) in izberite <guimenuitem>Prilepi</"
"guimenuitem>. To je odlična funkcija za izvoz delov diagrama kot preprostih "
"slik."

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exporting to an Image"
msgstr "Izvoz v sliko"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:19
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also export a complete diagram as an image. The only thing you need "
"to do is select the diagram you want to export, and then the option "
"<guimenuitem>Export as Picture...</guimenuitem> from the <guimenu>Diagram</"
"guimenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Izvozite lahko tudi celoten diagram kot sliko. Edina stvar, ki jo morate "
"storiti, je, da izberete diagram, ki ga želite izvoziti, in nato možnost "
"<guimenuitem>Izvozi kot sliko...</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Diagram</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can export multiple diagrams at once using the <guimenuitem>Export "
"Diagrams as Pictures...</guimenuitem> option from the <guimenu>File</"
"guimenu> menu. With this, you can also set the image resolution, so that the "
"images won't be as blurry."
msgstr ""
"Izvozite lahko več diagramov hkrati z možnostjo <guimenuitem>Izvozi diagrame "
"kot slike...</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>. S tem lahko "
"nastavite tudi ločljivost slike, tako da slike ne bodo tako zamegljene."

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "Printing"
msgstr "Tiskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&umbrello; allows you to print individual diagrams. Press the "
"<guiicon>Print</guiicon> button on the application toolbar or selecting the "
"<guimenuitem>Print</guimenuitem> option from the <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"menu will give you a standard &kde; Print dialog from where you can print "
"your diagrams."
msgstr ""
"&umbrello; omogoča tiskanje posameznih diagramov. Pritisnite gumb "
"<guiicon>Natisni</guiicon> v orodni vrstici aplikacije ali izberite možnost "
"<guimenuitem>Natisni</guimenuitem> v meniju <guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu>, da "
"dobite standardno &kde; Pogovorno okno za tiskanje, kjer lahko natisnete "
"svoje diagrame."

#. Tag: title
#: other_features.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "Logical Folders"
msgstr "Logične mape"

#. Tag: para
#: other_features.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To better organize your model, especially for larger projects, you can "
"create logical folders in the Tree View. Just select the option "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>New</guimenu><guimenuitem>Folder</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> from the context menu of the default folders in the Tree View to "
"create them. Folders can be nested, and you can move objects around by "
"dragging them from one folder and dropping them into another."
msgstr ""
"Za boljšo organizacijo modela, zlasti za večje projekte, lahko ustvarite "
"logične mape v drevesnem pogledu. Preprosto izberite možnost "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nova</guimenu><guimenuitem>Mapa</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> v kontekstnem meniju privzetih map v drevesnem pogledu, da jih "
"ustvarite. Mape so lahko ugnezdene, predmete pa lahko premikate tako, da jih "
"povlečete iz ene mape in spustite v drugo."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: other_features.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Organizing your Model with Folders"
msgstr "Organiziranje vašega modela z mapami"

